 3- ḥty̱ ậkẖr ạlḥyạẗ ạ̉htf mrnmaⁿạ
 qd ḍmnt ly ạlhnạ fy ạlṭryq mnʿmaⁿạ</lyrics>
<title>ạ̉frḥ fy kl ḥyn</title>
